WEBVTT

00:00:13.758 --> 00:00:16.040
I am going to start with a challenge.

00:00:16.040 --> 00:00:18.830
I want you to imagine each of these two scenes

00:00:18.830 --> 00:00:21.878
in as much detail as you can.

00:00:21.878 --> 00:00:23.260
Scene number one:

00:00:23.260 --> 00:00:25.925
"They gave us a hearty welcome."

00:00:25.925 --> 00:00:29.344
Well, who are the people who are giving a hearty welcome?

00:00:29.344 --> 00:00:30.838
What are they wearing?